{"about_the_game":"Deep Mine Is a 2D exploration and mining game in a procedurally generated world!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659110/extras/description_image_01.png?t=1717692004\" /><br><br>You are a dwarf in the mines deep in the mountains. Your goal ? To mine minerals to get richer and improve your tools. But be careful ! A demon sleeps in the deep, and making to much noise while mining might awaken it... Maybe one day, you will be strong enough to fight it... Maybe during your exploration you will have the opportunity to find your old colony and prove them that you are an incredible explorer !<br><br>Mine, fight, craft and build in this 2D survival game ! You are free to do whatever you want, as long as you do not awaken the demon of the mountains...<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore in a procedurally generated world.</strong> Each world is different and randomly generated.<br></li><li><strong>4 Player local-coop!</strong> You can play with up to 4 players in split screen.<br></li><li><strong>Lots of items to craft or buy.</strong> With over 17 different objects to vary the gameplay.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2659110/extras/description_image_02.png?t=1717692004\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Improve you character.</strong> As you get richer buy selling your gems, you will be able to improve your character skillset.<br></li><li><strong>Beware of the demon!</strong> Your exploration is not without risk. If you are not careful enough, you can awaken a demon that will spice up your exploration.<br></li><li><strong>Controller support.</strong> Xbox, Playstation and even Nintendo Switch controller support.]</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2659110?t=1717692004","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it